                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Share wins, strategies, and lessons learned</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Find collaboration partners and referrals</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Stay motivated and accountable</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Access to exclusive job boards and client leads</li>
